                    82.0,
                    1432.0
                ]
            ]
        },
        {
            "block_label": "text",
            "block_content": "Our required capital (“Required Capital”) estimation is based on the Required Capital framework, an internal capital adequacy measure. Common equity attribution to the business segments is based on capital usage calculated under the Required Capital framework, as well as each business segment's relative contribution to our total Required Capital.\nAverage Common Equity Attribution under the Required Capital Framework $ ^{1} $",
